---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Photos";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <h2>On Deck</h2>

  <p>
    To simulate the photo galleries I once maintained on Flickr and Instagram I plan to create a custom photo gallery to
    display my favorite shots from the past decade or two.
  </p>

  <p>
    Possibly using Cloudinary for image hosting, lightboxes, lazy-loaded images, full image downloads, collections based
    on themes. Also captions, descriptions, and metadata for each photo.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
